OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsettled, cloud spreading southwards
OL,7,Facross the whole of the region by the
OL,8,Fmorning with some fog patches over the
OL,9,FDerbyshire hills. Winds becoming light
OL,10,Fand variable. Feeling cooler overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA dry but cloudy morning.
OL,13,FCloudy breaking from late morning
OL,14,Fallowing sunny spells to develop.
OL,15,FClear again overnight. Winds becoming
OL,16,Flight and variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
